-- Manchester United’s Valencia to Miss Month With Hamstring Injury
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-02-16T20:58:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-16/manchester-united-s-valencia-to-miss-month-with-hamstring-injury.html
Manchester United winger  Antonio
Valencia  will be sidelined up to one month with a hamstring
injury, the Premier League club said on its website.  Valencia was injured while helping to set up  Javier
Hernandez ’s goal late in the second half of tonight’s 2-0 Europa
League win at Ajax. He was immediately replaced by  Danny
Welbeck .  Valencia has scored four goals in 27 games this season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  